  development of <mixer var="GAP"/>.
</p>

<h3>
  Contents
</h3>
<p>
  The data library of basic groups provides generic functions to construct
</p>
<ul>
  <li> cyclic groups, </li>
  <li> abelian groups, </li>
  <li> elementary abelian groups, </li>
  <li> dihedral groups, </li>
  <li> extraspecial groups, </li>
  <li> alternating groups, </li>
  <li> symmetric groups, </li>
  <li> Mathieu groups, </li>
  <li> Suzuki groups, and </li>
  <li> Ree groups. </li>
</ul>

